prefix every /(location)/ with www.yinlinhai.com

NOTE: you'll need to login at www.yinlinhai.com/html/login.htm to setup a session

/assignments/get

    METHOD: GET
    Returns a list of assignments


/assignments/

    METHOD: POST
    FORMAT:
        name=name of the assignment
        start-date=start date of the assignment
        end-date=end date of the assignment
    Required: name
    Creates an assignment


/assignments/(assignmentID)/get
    
    METHOD: GET
    Returns the list of questions associated with the assignment given
    assignmentID


/assignments/(assignmentID)/

    METHOD: POST
    FORMAT:
        name=name of the question
        type=type of the question (multiple-choice, short-answer)
        question=the full question
        answer=the answer of the question
    REQUIRED: question, answer, type
    Creates a question in the assignment given by AssignmentID


/assignments/(assignmentID)/(questionID)/

    METHOD: POST
    FORMAT:
        name=name of the question
        type=type of the question (multiple-choice, short-answer)
        question=the full question
        answer=the answer of the question
    REQUIRED: question, answer, type
    Edits an existing question in the assignment given by AssignmentID, QuestionID
